ability.name: lingering-aroma
ability.short_effect: Contact changes the attacker's Ability to Lingering Aroma.

ability.name: seed-sower
ability.short_effect: Turns the ground into Grassy Terrain when the Pokémon is hit by an attack.

ability.name: thermal-exchange
ability.short_effect: Raises Attack when hit by a Fire-type move. Cannot be burned.

ability.name: anger-shell
ability.short_effect: When the Pokémon's HP drops below half, Anger Shell lowers its Defense and Special Defense but its Attack, Special Attack and Speed are raised.

ability.name: purifying-salt
ability.short_effect: Protects from status conditions and halves damage from Ghost-type moves.

ability.name: well-baked-body
ability.short_effect: Immune to Fire-type moves, and Defense is sharply boosted.

ability.name: wind-rider
ability.short_effect: Gives immunity to wind moves, and causes the Pokémon's Attack to increase by one stage when hit by one.

ability.name: guard-dog
ability.short_effect: Boosts Attack if intimidated, and prevents being forced to switch out.

ability.name: rocky-payload
ability.short_effect: Powers up Rock-type moves.

ability.name: wind-power
ability.short_effect: When hit by a wind move, the power of the next Electric-type move it uses is doubled.

ability.name: zero-to-hero
ability.short_effect: Transforms into its Hero Form when switching out.

ability.name: commander
ability.short_effect: Goes inside the mouth of an ally Dondozo if one is on the field.

ability.name: electromorphosis
ability.short_effect: When hit by an attack, the power of the next Electric-type move it uses is doubled.

ability.name: protosynthesis
ability.short_effect: Raises highest stat in harsh sunlight, or if holding Booster Energy.

ability.name: quark-drive
ability.short_effect: Raises highest stat on Electric Terrain, or if holding Booster Energy.

ability.name: good-as-gold
ability.short_effect: Gives immunity to status moves.

ability.name: vessel-of-ruin
ability.short_effect: Lowers Special Attack of all Pokémon except itself.

ability.name: sword-of-ruin
ability.short_effect: Lowers Defense of all Pokémon except itself.

ability.name: tablets-of-ruin
ability.short_effect: Lowers Attack of all Pokémon except itself.

ability.name: beads-of-ruin
ability.short_effect: Lowers Special Defense of all Pokémon except itself.

ability.name: orichalcum-pulse
ability.short_effect: Turns the sunlight harsh when entering battle, and boosts Attack while active.

ability.name: hadron-engine
ability.short_effect: Creates an Electric Terrain when entering battle, and boosts Special Attack while active.

ability.name: opportunist
ability.short_effect: Copies stat boosts by the opponent.

ability.name: cud-chew
ability.short_effect: Causes the Pokémon to reuse an already consumed Berry at the end of the next turn.

ability.name: sharpness
ability.short_effect: Powers up slicing moves.

ability.name: supreme-overlord
ability.short_effect: Attack and Special Attack are boosted for each party Pokémon that has been defeated.

ability.name: costar
ability.short_effect: Copies ally's stat changes on entering battle.

ability.name: toxic-debris
ability.short_effect: Scatters poison spikes at the feet of the opposing team when the Pokémon takes damage from physical moves.

ability.name: armor-tail
ability.short_effect: Prevents the opponent from using any moves that have priority, such as Quick Attack.

ability.name: earth-eater
ability.short_effect: Restores HP when hit by a Ground-type move.

ability.name: mycelium-might
ability.short_effect: Status moves go last, but are not affected by the opponent's ability.

ability.name: minds-eye
ability.short_effect: The Pokémon ignores changes to opponents' evasiveness, its accuracy can't be lowered, and it can hit Ghost types with Normal- and Fighting-type moves.

ability.name: supersweet-syrup
ability.short_effect: Once per battle, when a Pokémon with Supersweet Syrup enters the battle, it lowers the evasion stat of all adjacent opponents by one stage.

ability.name: hospitality
ability.short_effect: When a Pokémon with Hospitality enters a battle, it restores HP for an ally by 25%.

ability.name: toxic-chain
ability.short_effect: May cause bad poisoning when the Pokémon hits an opponent with a move.

ability.name: embody-aspect
ability.short_effect: Embody Aspect boosts a particular stat, depending on the form of a Terastallized Ogerpon

ability.name: tera-shift
ability.short_effect: When Terapagos enters the battle, it turns into its Terastal Form until the end of the battle.

ability.name: tera-shell
ability.short_effect: All damage-dealing moves that hit the Pokémon when its HP is full will not be very effective.

ability.name: teraform-zero
ability.short_effect: As soon as Terapagos assumes its Stellar Form, it will immediately neutralize weather and terrain effects.

ability.name: poison-puppeteer
ability.short_effect: Pokémon poisoned by Pecharunt's moves will also become confused.
